  "texts": [
    "For the overall published literature on LLMs in healthcare, there are more publications evaluating performance on public data.",
    "This includes performance on board examinations and question-answering based on guidelines (Sallam 2023).",
    "These analyses may introduce contamination of data, since LLMs were trained on vast data from the internet.",
    "For commercial models such as ChatGPT, the type of training data is not disclosed.",
    "Furthermore, these applications do not necessarily reflect on the performance of these models in real-world clinical settings."
  ],
